  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the butcher shop, where every object has its own story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This atmospheric <strong>point-and-click puzzle</strong> game puts you in the shoes of a mysterious butcher shop worker. Explore the surroundings, <strong>zoom in and out</strong> on details, and uncover hidden puzzles, secret levels, and things that go beyond the ordinary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No words, no hints — just you, the environment, and your <strong>attention to detail</strong>. Look closely around you. Everything is not as it seems.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the butcher shop, where every object has its own story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This atmospheric <strong>point-and-click puzzle</strong> game puts you in the shoes of a mysterious butcher shop worker. Explore the surroundings, <strong>zoom in and out</strong> on details, and uncover hidden puzzles, secret levels, and things that go beyond the ordinary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No words, no hints — just you, the environment, and your <strong>attention to detail</strong>. Look closely around you. Everything is not as it seems.</p>",
